OL,3,CPlan for GPs to divert millions of
OL,4,Cpatients from hospital waiting lists
OL,6,FGPs will be able to seek advice from
OL,7,Fspecialists before referring patients
OL,8,Fin a bid to cut hospital waiting
OL,9,Flists, the government has announced.
OL,11,FThe scheme is part of a government
OL,12,Fplan to divert up to two million
OL,13,Fpatients from NHS waiting lists in
OL,14,FEngland by the end of next year.
OL,16,FIt can mean patients are referred for
OL,17,Fblood tests and scans from their
OL,18,Fsurgery, or directed to other
OL,19,Fcommunity services, for the likes of
OL,20,Fphysio, rather than being added to NHS
OL,21,Fwaiting lists.
