OL,3,CPlan for GPs to divert millions of
OL,4,Cpatients from hospital waiting lists
OL,6,FMinisters said the move will "stop
OL,7,Fmasses of people" going to hospital
OL,8,Ffor "unnecessary appointments".
OL,10,FThose benefiting include women with
OL,11,Fsymptoms of the menopause and patients
OL,12,Fwith ear, throat and nose issues,
OL,13,Faccording to the Department of Health
OL,14,Fand Social Care.
OL,16,FGPs welcomed the announcement but said
OL,17,Fthe scheme must be properly resourced.
