OL,3,CPlan for GPs to divert millions of
OL,4,Cpatients from hospital waiting lists
OL,6,FThe expansion will also aim to
OL,7,Fstandardise its use across the country.
OL,9,FIt follows an announcement in January
OL,10,Fthat GPs would be offered #20 every
OL,11,Ftime they consult a specialist using
OL,12,Fthe scheme.
OL,14,FHealth minister Karin Smyth said: "By
OL,15,Fcaring for patients closer to home, we
OL,16,Fsave time and stop masses of people
OL,17,Fhaving to head to hospital for
OL,18,Funnecessary appointments in the first
OL,19,Fplace.
