OL,6,F"We are rewiring the NHS so that we
OL,7,Fare doing things differently, more
OL,8,Fefficiently and delivering better
OL,9,Foutcomes for patients.
OL,11,F"This scheme is a perfect example of
OL,12,Fhow we are saving patients time and
OL,13,Freducing pressure on key NHS services
OL,14,Fin the process."
OL,16,FAdvice and guidance has been used
OL,17,Fsince 2015, and the pathway was
OL,18,Fformalised by NHS England in 2021.
