OL,3,CPlan for GPs to divert millions of
OL,4,Cpatients from hospital waiting lists
OL,6,FAccording to DHSC, between July and
OL,7,FDecember last year about 660,000
OL,8,Ftreatments were diverted from
OL,9,Fhospitals to the community as a result
OL,10,Fof the advice and guidance scheme, up
OL,11,F60,000 for the same period in 2023.
OL,13,FProfessor Sir Sam Everington, who has
OL,14,Fbeen a GP in Tower Hamlets, east
OL,15,FLondon, since 1989, added: "Advice and
OL,16,Fguidance enables patients and GPs to
OL,17,Fget advice direct from a specialist,
OL,18,Ftypically within a week for routine
OL,19,Fcases.
