OL,6,F"This means that patients get their
OL,7,Fhealth problems sorted rapidly,
OL,8,Fpreventing health deterioration and
OL,9,Favoiding long waits to be seen.
OL,11,F"In my experience, over two-thirds of
OL,12,Fpatients with kidney disease can be
OL,13,Fmanaged in this way with advice from a
OL,14,Fconsultant and treatment by the GP,
OL,15,Fremoving the enormous stress and
OL,16,Funcertainty of waiting a long time."
