OL,4,Cpatients from hospital waiting lists
OL,6,FProfessor Kamila Hawthorne, chairwoman
OL,7,Fof the Royal College of GPs, said:
OL,8,F"Advice and guidance services have the
OL,9,Fpotential to support GPs to refer
OL,10,Fappropriately and deliver care to
OL,11,Fpatients whilst they are waiting for
OL,12,Fspecialist treatment, but it's crucial
OL,13,Fthat GP services have the capacity to
OL,14,Faccommodate the shift from hospitals
OL,15,Fto community care so this funding is a
OL,16,Fgood step in the right direction.
OL,26,@pD@AOU
