OL,3,CPlan for GPs to divert millions of
OL,4,Cpatients from hospital waiting lists
OL,6,F"In the past, some GPs have reported
OL,7,Fissues with using A&G services,
OL,8,Fincluding that they shift care into
OL,9,Fgeneral practice without appropriate
OL,10,Fresource, and that they can be used to
OL,11,Freject necessary referrals.
OL,13,F"We have always been supportive of the
OL,14,FGovernment's aspiration to shift more
OL,15,Fcare into the community, and an
OL,16,Fincreasing use of A&G services may
OL,17,Fhelp enable this, as long as it is
OL,18,Fproperly resourced across the country.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
