OL,3,CPlan for GPs to divert millions of
OL,4,Cpatients from hospital waiting lists
OL,6,F"Funding must follow the patient, and
OL,7,Fwe need to see significant investment
OL,8,Fin general practice, following years
OL,9,Fof underfunding by successive
OL,10,Fgovernments, so we can deliver safe,
OL,11,Ftimely and appropriate care to our
OL,12,Fpatients close to home."
OL,14,FRachel Power, chief executive of the
OL,15,FPatients Association, welcomed the
OL,16,Fannouncement, and said it is a "step
OL,17,Fin the right direction" but that "the
OL,18,Fsuccess of the scheme will depend on
OL,19,Fgenuine partnership between patients,
OL,20,FGPs, and specialists".
