OL,6,F"Patients must be equal partners in
OL,7,Fconversations about their care, with
OL,8,Fthe agency and power to take part in
OL,9,Fshared decision-making that recognises
OL,10,Ftheir expertise in their own lives,"
OL,11,Fshe added.
OL,13,F"To make this work, we need
OL,14,Ftransparency around how GP capacity
OL,15,Fchallenges will be addressed, and we
OL,16,Fneed to see proper investment in
OL,17,Fresources, training, and support for
OL,18,Fshared decision-making.
